com.siperian.sif.message

Class XrefKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.XrefKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class XrefKey
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Key containing information to identify an Xref record uniquely.

    Use in classes that extend SiperianRequest or SiperianResponse to store key data for Xref tables

    For non version BO an xref key is composed of the following required fields: *
    • Source system that the xref data comes from
    • Primary key of the data from the source system
    For version BO an xref key is composed of the following required fields:
    • Source system that the xref data comes from
    • Primary key of the data from the source system
    • Period start Date
    • Period end Date
    • Rowid Xref
    Or
    See Also:
